Acked-by: Florian Fainelli <f.fainelli@gmail.com>
Acked-by: Adrian Hunter <adrian.hunter@intel.com>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20220427180853.35970-3-kdasu.kdev@gmail.com
